overview: Tampa was home to CF longer than anywhere else, and while we got our start in Kansas City and found our way to Vegas it’s really in Tampa that we made a name for ourselves and became the site and brand we are today. As part of our 10th anniversary celebrations, we took a bunch of CF studs back to our old Florida home to see how the city’s changed, hang out, visit some old friends, and film some insanely hot action! Connor, Quinn, Rowan, Zeb, Brayden, and Kenny join us on this journey back to Tampa to get it on with one another, relive some old memories, and make some incredible new ones!
title: Coming of Age in Tampa
